#: src/octoprint/plugins/tracking/templates/snippets/trackingDescription.jinja2:1
msgid ""
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"    Anonymous usage tracking provides valuable insights into how many "
"instances running what versions of OctoPrint are out there,\n"
"    whether they are successfully completing print jobs and various other"
" metrics.\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    By enabling it you help to identify problems with new releases and "
"release candidates early on, and to better\n"
"    tailor OctoPrint's future development to actual use.\n"
"</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<p>\n"
"    O rastreamento anônimo de uso fornece insights valiosos sobre quantas instâncias executando quais versões do OctoPrint existem,\n"
"    se elas estão completando com sucesso os trabalhos de impressão e várias outras métricas.\n"
"</p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"    Ao habilitá-lo, você ajuda a identificar problemas com novos lançamentos e release candidates no início, e a melhor\n"
"    adaptar o desenvolvimento futuro do OctoPrint ao uso real.\n"
"</p>\n"

#: src/octoprint/plugins/tracking/templates/snippets/trackingDetails.jinja2:1
msgid ""
"\n"
"    For details on what gets tracked, please refer to <a "
"href=\"https://tracking.octoprint.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">tracking.octoprint.org</a>\n"
"    and also the <a href=\"https://tracking.octoprint.org/privacy\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Privacy Policy at "
"tracking.octoprint.org</a>.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Para detalhes sobre o que é rastreado, consulte <a "
"href=\"https://tracking.octoprint.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener "
"noreferrer\">tracking.octoprint.org</a>\n"
"    e também a <a href=\"https://tracking.octoprint.org/privacy\" "
"target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Política de Privacidade em "
"tracking.octoprint.org</a>.\n"

